705948f-a.title: Brooklyn: Nevins Street - State Street
705948f-a.text:
Nevins Street, at the N.W. corner of State Street, showing the Harriet Judson Y.W.C.A. and Junior League House.
April 24, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

706877f-a.title: Brooklyn: State Street - Nevins Street
706877f-a.text:
4544 to 468 State Street, at, adjoining and east of the S. E. corner of Nevins Street. These are typical houses
of this area.
June 15, 1940
P. L. Sperr
